io.oauth

Class OAuthRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.oauth.OAuthRequest

  • public abstract class OAuthRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    The OAuthRequest class contains abstract method you can implement to set your http request's url and add headers to inject your oauth tokens.
